{"tid":1578735,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"莎莎國際發盈警 8月份銷售表現急挫28%","createTime":"2019-09-18T08:57:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T10:46:29.000Z","uid":39464,"like":86,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"f8cb319d470449be6077609501fae22f1c4bcf80","tid":1578735,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:57:42.000Z","msg":"莎莎國際（0178）發盈警。集團指，截至今年8月底止5個月，集團營業額約為30億元，較去年同期下跌約15%，其中港澳市場亦下跌17%，當中8月份的銷售表現最差，按年下降約28%，而港澳市場亦於同月跌32%，相關跌幅令港澳市場及集團於8月份錄得虧損，亦引致集團首5個月錄得虧損。<br />\n<br />\n另外，集團銷售情況於9月份仍然非常疲弱。本月首15日，集團營業額按月跌約14%，按年跌約29%。上一個財政年度，集團截至9月30日止6個月期間的溢利為2.029億元。<br />\n<br />\n集團解釋，業績倒退的主要原因是香港地區的銷售表現疲軟，受到香港持續不斷的社會活動、中美貿易戰升温及人民幣貶值所影響，導致來自內地的訪港遊客銳減，消費意欲減退，繼而打擊銷售。<br />\n<br />\n莎莎今日收報1.71元，跌0.58%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1568796458860&amp;issue=20190918\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1568796458860%26issue%3D20190918&d=Ii72mHdDrz30Fn2z87Evj67XYz%2BrpCtmef%2B4BlhZTRs%3D&h=79ae8552\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1568796458860%26issue%3D20190918&h=93a2b404\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1568796458860&amp;issue=20190918</a>"},{"pid":"bbacddd14ba6d8c65ed9cdd99ea032bcb4a500ae","tid":1578735,"uid":117906,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:58:34.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全球響應「929全球集會抗赤納粹」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全世界一齊對準極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577380</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWqVmOV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWqVmOV.jpg&h=075c7745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1tov9s.